\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uqw6gCjXqUY</a><br />\n<br />\ndavie504回過一條片話dragonforce好勁, 不過基於bass最勁, davie504挑戰herman li用bass彈dragonforce代表作<br />\n之後herman li出片要求davie先學佢自己潛水彈樂器再講<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ixlFCdlz5SI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DixlFCdlz5SI&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=32e33c33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ixlFCdlz5SI</a><br />\nps後來davie504有再出片話herman li唔係咁玩架, 你(herman li)完成咗我(davie504)當初提出黎嘅挑戰我(davie504)就跟機潛水彈bass<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n期間dragon force評論過davie504同twosetviolin之間嘅片<br />\n跟手一齊玩加入戰爭, 瘋狂笑鳩davie504<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yASmgl3cPe4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyASmgl3cPe4&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=1772b530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yASmgl3cPe4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nthe doo都有玩埋一份<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZOiAZlAK3ZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZOiAZlAK3ZE&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=56a9365c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZOiAZlAK3ZE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由鬥膠到認真較勁到假膠&quot;fake&quot;到好似堅黎料, davie504一個挑起成場戰爭一打三, 好精彩好好笑"},{"pid":"ae461fe6f3e1a010f6a5ee88019133efa4322757","tid":2128162,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T19:20:14.000Z","msg":"我又係day one 開始睇<br />\n笑撚到傻呀 !"},{"pid":"7f16d188c273fa22892a9c775bb3b3c50bb77ab1","tid":2128162,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae461fe6f3e1a010f6a5ee88019133efa4322757","tid":2128162,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T19:20:14.000Z","msg":"我又係day one 開始睇<br />\n笑撚到傻呀 !"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T19:22:34.000Z","msg":"邊